ummm...no. 1 1/2 sticks of butter IS 3/4 cup (6oz). 3 sticks of butter is 3/4lb. there are 4 sticks of butter (4oz - 1/2cup each) in a lb (16oz) so each stick is 1/4lb - 3 sticks would be 3/4lb. Hope that helps...

